{"tid":1745393,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"陳奕迅2003年大預言！！","createTime":"2019-11-22T07:53:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T10:17:45.000Z","uid":253240,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e3b381cac1e094015aa84202b7b6812075bb2b6d","tid":1745393,"uid":253240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:53:35.000Z","msg":"原來Eason 2003年已經有首咁既歌<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小孩不懂怕<br />\n作詞：陳文剛     作曲：阿飛<br />\n編曲：阿飛, 胡波 監製：陳奕迅, 阿飛, 胡波<br />\n<br />\n為這世界別再亂打<br />\n請你倆位聽下 不用調查<br />\n別向世界亂說著鬼話<br />\n哪會有人信 將戰鬥停下<br />\n<br />\n人肉大爆炸 連累到百姓害怕 還請你收手吧<br />\n無謂將好好的家鄉 繁華變敗瓦<br />\n誰都不想失去家 誰變得孤和寡 風吹雨打<br />\n誰也都不想天天驚怕 害怕轉間遭轟炸<br />\n<br />\n小孩還不懂怕 攜炸彈出戰不需驚訝<br />\n別再扮得相當瀟灑<br />\n<br />\n望見每個父母淚灑 呼叫到聲沙啞 手腳亂爬<br />\n別當百姓像個活標靶 你有冇人性 請你快停下<br />\n<br />\n人肉大爆炸 連累到百姓害怕 還請你收手吧<br />\n無謂將好好的家鄉 繁華變敗瓦<br />\n誰都不想失去家 誰變得孤和寡 風吹雨打<br />\n誰也都不想天天驚怕 害怕轉間遭轟炸<br />\n<br />\n小孩還不懂怕 攜炸彈出戰不需驚訝<br />\n父母是否講真心話<br />\n<br />\n小孩還不懂怕 攜炸彈出戰不需驚訝<br />\n別再扮得相當瀟洒"},{"pid":"7f72b33396e95bb0c5f389000f8f077bfd400fb7","tid":1745393,"uid":178800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T07:54:58.000Z","msg":"E神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fee88255c98b68d82fd073e1def80a65086058b","tid":1745393,"uid":195030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T09:21:11.000Z","msg":"中曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"596823f01d11dfcb13f97271b55ad4eac74ebfa5","tid":1745393,"uid":54656,"like":1,"dislike